"{\"uid\": \"etonline.com-hoda-kotb-says-celine-dion-is-planning-a-surprise-return-performance-talks-paris-olympics-228840\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Hoda Kotbis sharing some illuminating comments that happened behind-the-scenes during her emotional interview withC\\u00e9line Dion.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\", \"score\": 0.5882352802234031, \"rank\": 0.6999999999999931, \"text\": \"Hoda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_(given_name)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 59-year-oldTodayco-hostsat down with the 56-year-old Canadian pop icon in Juneto discussher health battle with Stiff Person Syndromeand her future as she navigates her medical struggles.\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.4971275429133837, \"rank\": 0.7998056235134868, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"First of all, she's an incredible fighter.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had no idea what she had been through, how close she came at some point to actually not surviving it,\\\" Kotb shared of Dion on Tuesday'sWatch What Happens Live With Andy Cohen.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Cohen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3085398983693462e-24, \"text\": \"Andy Cohen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Cohen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Cohen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And now here she is, and she's singing again.\\\"\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion shared with Kotb that singing with her medical condition felt\\\"like being strangled,\\\" and causes parts of her body to spasm.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Living withStiff Person Syndromewas\\u00a0so intense for Dion at times that it caused her to break a rib.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It can be in the abdominal.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can be in the spine, in the ribs.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it feels like if I point my feet, it will stay in it,\\\" Dion explained to Kotb.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Or if I cook, my fingers or my hands will get in position.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's cramping, but it's like you are in the position of you cannot unlock them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb did tease after their interview that Dion had plans to return to the stage for a live performance.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So when a caller asked the journalist what she knew about this potential appearance, Kotb spilled some tea onWWHL.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her manager was off-camera, and I was like, 'So what's going on?\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When are you performing again?'\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And she goes, 'Can I tell her?'\\\"\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb shared, adopting Dion's accent.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And her manager goes, 'No!'\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He screams, 'No.'\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like, there is something.\\\"\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The caller questioned whether that appearance might take place during the upcomingParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb admitted to not knowing for sure, but said she thought that would be \\\"spectacular.\\\"\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That would be amazing!\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, I just got chills,\\\" Kotb'sTodayco-host, Savannah Guthrie, exclaimed.\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_Guthrie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Savannah Guthrie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_Guthrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Savannah_Guthrie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That would be amazing, but I do not know,\\\" Kotb added.\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know she's going to be performing live again, though.\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know where.\\\"\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Getting a bit carried away with the notion, Guthrie gushed, \\\"It has to be the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2047, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woody_Guthrie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.08656553077351e-15, \"text\": \"Guthrie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woody_Guthrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woody_Guthrie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That would be incredible.\\\"\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However,WWHLhost Andy Cohen was more skeptical, noting, \\\"I think it's not gonna be and here's why.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Cohen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3085398983693462e-24, \"text\": \"Andy Cohen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Cohen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Cohen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it would be amazing, but my understanding is that this is something she can not control.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so if it was something so set...\\\"  Kotb challenged that idea, sharing that Dion has found a more manageable regimen of medications she takes, saying, \\\"So you never know.\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, if she knows she's performing at a certain hour, let us do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theMayo Clinic, Stiff Person Syndrome is \\\"a rare disorder of motor function characterized by involuntary stiffness of axial muscles and superimposed painful muscle spasms, which are often induced by startle or emotional stimuli.\\\"\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotbopened up to ETabout Dion's coping mechanisms on stage when she first started experiencing symptoms of Stiff Person Syndrome.\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She would sing her songs and then she would take the microphone and put it out to the crowd,\\\" Kotb told ET last month.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why?\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To get a break.\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her fans were helping her.\\\"\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When COVID-19 hit, Kotb said it was \\\"weirdly a blessing\\\" for Dion \\\"because now she could heal, she could stop, she could be home.\\\"\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, during that time at home,Dion canceledher remaining\\u00a0Courage World Tour dates due to \\\"severe and persistent muscle spasms.\\\"\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, Dion entered into a self-imposed isolation of sorts.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is used to singing for big crowds, so since she could not sing, she said she did not want to go outside and be with her children because people would say, 'Oh, she seemed fine with her kids... Why wasn't she on stage?\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to get my money back for my ticket,'\\\" Kotb said of Dion, whoshared sonsRen\\u00e9-Charles, 23, Nelson, 13, and Eddy, 13, with her late husband,\\u00a0Ren\\u00e9 Ang\\u00e9lil.\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3761, \"end\": 3767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelson_Muntz\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.838464847958164e-13, \"text\": \"Nelson\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelson_Muntz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelson_Muntz\"}, {\"begin\": 3810, \"end\": 3822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ren\\u00e9_Ang\\u00e9lil\", \"score\": 0.9999999108436026, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ren\\u00e9 Ang\\u00e9lil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ren\\u00e9_Ang\\u00e9lil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ren\\u00e9_Ang\\u00e9lil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was so concerned about [her fans], so it was kind of an isolation where she was living,\\\" Kotb added.\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was learning to work with a PT to keep her muscles limber to know what to do when something starts to to cramp up.\\\"\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 4051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion documented her health journey in the Prime Video docuseries,I Am: Celine Dion.\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED CONTENT:  Video  News  Music  News  News\", \"from\": 4138, \"to\": 4186, \"entities\": []}]}"